        <strong>Fatigue Reduction</strong>
        <p>Chronic fatigue symptoms improved in 63% of participants over 90 days<br /><em>J Ethnopharmacol, 2012</em></p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="warn-box">
      <span class="warn-box-ico">&#9888;</span>
      <p><strong>Important context:</strong> Most shilajit research uses purified, standardized extracts (particularly PrimaVie) at specific doses. Non-standardized products may not deliver equivalent results. The testosterone studies specifically used 250mg of PrimaVie — a product with documented fulvic acid content above 50%. Shilajit products without fulvic acid standardization cannot be assumed to produce the same effects.</p>
    </div>

